==Recording Accordion==

===General techniques===
'''Each technique is defined with a bullet point.'''

*Place a [[microphone]] 2-3 feet away from the bellows of the instrument 
*Place a large diaphragm condenser microphone pointed at the keyboard side about a foot away. 
*Clip a a miniature condenser tie-tack microphone to the wrist strap of the accordion 

----

===Cajun Accordion===

*A SM57 capsule on a bracket at the bottom of the accordion facing upward is a standard mic techniques for this instrument.

